name: Release 1.8.4
body:
## Fixes:
1. Search works with multiple apps with the same name
1. Search fixed to run proper app

name: Release 1.8.3
body:
## New features:
1. Discoverable swipe to all apps (arrow icon)
1. Icon is clickable

name: Release 1.8.2
body:
## Fixes:
1. System nav draws over launcher in Android 10
1. Duplicate name bug - no possibility to run second app with the same name
1. Fixed bug for onClick and onLongClick in InstalledApps

name: Release 1.8.0
body:
## New features:
1. Search box on all apps view

name: Release 1.7.1
body:
## Fixes:
1. Reloads all apps only when needed

name: Release 1.7.0
body:
## New features:
1. Favourite app removal confirmation dialog
1. It's now impossible to put duplicates on favourites view

## Fixes:
1. Right padding
1. Black screen on back button
1. All apps view loads faster (as it's loaded on resume of favourites view)

name: Release 1.6.4
body:
## Fixes:
1. Speed up the all apps view launch (now it's slow only for first run)

name: Release 1.6.2
body:
## Fixes:
1. Highlight on long press at Favourites view
1. Change timing of highlight on click

name: Release 1.6.1
body:
## New features:
1. System wallpaper support
1. New highlight of the selected items
1. "+" instead "+ add favorite app" if there is at least one favourite app
1. Animated slide transition since Android 2.0
1. New features alert support

## Fixes:
1. No more accidental long press on all apps view

name: Release 1.4
body:
## New features:
1. Swipe animation
1. Immersive and transparent status bar on all apps view

## Fixes:
1. Top padding
1. Crash on "+ add application" long press

name: Release 1.3
body:
## New features:
1. Allow more than 5 apps on home screen
1. Use dark theme for app picker
1. Dim system bars (API level 14)
1. Set padding based on screen width instead of fixed value
1. Replaced "EMPTY" text button to more descriptive

## Bug fixes:
1. Fix app sorting in 'Pick an app' dialog
1. Fix wording of launch error
1. Fix error with low profile mode

name: Release 1.1
body:
## New features
1. editing two first slots feature

name: Release 1.0
body:
# New features

1. home screen with 5 favourite apps. 
1. 3 configurable favourites slots
1. all apps on swipe left
